| Asset | Host | URL |
|---|---|---|
| Landing page | GitHub Pages (`/docs` on `main`) | `https://hannojacobs.github.io/DICTATR/` |
| DMG download | GitHub Releases | `https://github.com/HannoJacobs/DICTATR/releases/latest/download/DICTATR.dmg` |
